  keywords      = {Acoustic Stimulation/adverse effects; Animals; Auditory Cortex/*physiology; Auditory Pathways/*physiology; Auditory Perception/*physiology; Brain Mapping/*methods; Hearing Loss/*physiopathology; Learning/*physiology; Neuronal Plasticity/*physiology},
